                <h1>New infrastructure coming to Raleigh-Durham International Airport, but not without criticism </h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/39b9dd05-a7f3-4b2c-857b-591003140f03.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="&lt;p&gt;The&#x20;long-term&#x20;expansion&#x20;plan&#x20;for&#x20;the&amp;nbsp&#x3B;Raleigh-Durham&#x20;International&#x20;Airport&#x20;features&#x20;the&#x20;creation&#x20;of&#x20;a&#x20;new&#x20;runway&#x20;and&#x20;23&#x20;new&#x20;terminal&#x20;gates.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            <p>The long-term expansion plan for the&nbsp;Raleigh-Durham International Airport features the creation of a new runway and 23 new terminal gates.</p>

                            
                        </div>
                    </figure>
                
                                    <div class="row  mt-4 mb-0 mb-md-4">
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                            <aside class="author-name">
                                    
    
                                    
            By <a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/staff/bre-bradham">Bre Bradham</a>
                                    
                                <div class="mt-1">
                                    <span class="can-localize">October 24, 2016 | 12:25am EDT</span>
                                </div>
                            </aside>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6 text-left text-md-right d-print-none">
                            <ul class="social-links list-unsyled list-inline mt-4 mt-md-0">
                                <li class="list-inline-item"><a href="http://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=https://www.dukechronicle.com/article/2016/10/new-infrastructure-coming-to-raleigh-durham-international-airport-but-not-without-criticism" target="_blank" class="sends-events" data-ga-category="Share" data-ga-action="click" data-ga-label="facebook" data-ga-value="CURL"><i class="fab fa-facebook"></i></a></li>
